{"tid":1632112,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"梁天琦：懇請不要被仇恨支配自己","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T00:15:53.000Z","uid":85924,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d60e1b45dd02edf61cacd70317f747ace3f5c5d0","tid":1632112,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"無可否認7婆出招之後風向好亂，大家一時間都未必適應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係請大家放一放慢，諗好前面點行先再衝。我地咁多個月一路走來係靠<span style=\"color: red;\">創意、流水抗爭、適當既勇武去贏民心、贏輿論。</span>（你話我民意撚都係咁話）<br />\n<br />\n我地持續得越耐，政府越頭痕。政府最想我地速戰速決，我地偏唔可以咁做。時間係我地個邊，人民係我地個邊，慢慢打就會贏。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">懇請不要被仇恨支配自己。</span></span>"},{"pid":"38cc2289bb5c89611675fb71a8bc9c119ca139cf","tid":1632112,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee11e070fb0fc49e621ca4301995da6fecbb2b2b","tid":1632112,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048d39143fdd83feb42e2ab980b85aa5500d6309","tid":1632112,"uid":287211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:35.000Z","msg":"越亂 証明林鄭越有用去平亂<br />\n<br />\n越亂就想美國唔好企我們呢到 影響法案辣度<br />\n<br />\n我們拉長嚟玩 條臭西趁越亂 乘機出師有名推其他法<br />\n<br />\n冚家產 蒙面法之後 佢點到會贏<br />\n<br />\n1） 更亂 可推其他乜撚緊急法 96小時乜春之類法<br />\n<br />\n2） 平靜咗 証明條蒙面法係有用 回復少少秩序之類<br />\n<br />\n所以條臭西點都贏<br />\n<br />\n但我地冷靜下先 亂同平靜D的結果 邊個畫面達到制裁目標容易些？ 當然我假設大家想班狗賊同我們欖炒! 記得謝蛇移民case? 呢D先至係我哋要的清算目標！<br />\n<br />\n所以 忍一下先 唔好比條臭西帶到我哋！<br />\n<br />\n我不是叫大家晤搞 只是拉長嚟玩 有先後次序<br />\n<br />\n我哋翻新黨鐵計劃延遲二三星期 黨鐡仲會係到 所以押後一下！ 大家想想！"},{"pid":"fc138d359eceff0701922cd2037291c34faa45ce","tid":1632112,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"695fcba420ff0ca14fcc4f8b8643541cb9c7792d","tid":1632112,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723b62d4d5a7f2ae492f54171d33fd523a8271e7","tid":1632112,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"23f3349aa796286b73dc1920c0d108ef755c6be6","tid":1632112,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:46.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1af3c08a836f5a1463e9ec97ccf64db9769323d1","tid":1632112,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:18.000Z","msg":"咁撚多bot既"},{"pid":"4b8fd3a32dfb7cb08a5960e7ab7b32d92c5b5eaa","tid":1632112,"uid":248949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:29.000Z","msg":"天琦行得太前，今次大家要跟好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb76d07fee95a37101380eb606c0d17321f7962","tid":1632112,"uid":30988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:46.000Z","msg":"我不欲受傷，更不欲兄弟受傷。<br />\n如果令惡人受傷可以捍衛兄弟，我義不容辭。<br />\n為了這世界的和平與自由，人有時是要拿起槍技的，<br />\n正如二戰時邱吉爾所選擇的道路。<br />\n<br />\n即使可能會有衝突，或許會有人傷亡，但你請放心。我們並沒有被仇恨衝昏頭腦。相反，我們很清醒，心中只有愛。對香港的愛，對所有市民的愛，甚至，對黑警的愛 -- 如果這樣做可以幫助這群黑警冷靜下來，不再行使警暴去徒添圍毆殺人強姦的孽障，這就是對這幫加害者的愛。<br />\n政府說要止暴制亂，其實抗爭者也是要止暴制亂，止的是警暴，制的是警亂。三個月來，大家都明白暴力的源頭正正是來自警隊。不論藍黃請撫心自問﹕是抗爭者頭破血流的多還是警察頭破血流的多？是抗爭者被爆眼骨折的多還是警察被爆眼骨折的多？是警察在非禮強姦輪姦抗爭者，抗爭者有非禮強姦輪姦警察嗎？沒有。<br />\n有人可能會懷疑，當抗爭者的棍棒反擊在黑警的頭上時，我們是否失去了同情心？<br />\n不，我們所為正是因為同情心。只是我們的同情心更大的用於被害者身上，而不是放在加害者身上。只要能夠阻止黑警濫暴，就可以保護現場的手足，讓他們反思過往的暴行，乃至防止日後更多無辜的市民受害。這才是同情心的正確使用方法。<br />\n很多左翼、甚至大多數黃絲都明白，「暴力不能解決問題」。不明白這個道理的是政府和黑警。這三個月來，他們賴以維持權力的就是暴力。對黑警使用暴力，正正是要教育他們，「暴力是不能解決問題的」。你可以對手無寸鐵者，以壓倒性的武力暴力打擊我們，但不要忘記，你們的武力並非每天24 小時都在守護你們。每次你們的臥底落單、每次你們沒有武器在身，每次你們在廣大的香港市民之中時，你們都有可能被暴力所反噬。黑警們不明白的話，總有一天會發生一些事讓你們明白的。<br />\n當政府和民間、黑警和抗爭者、暴政和公民都了解暴力的本質時，真正的和平與公義就會來臨。港共與中共都需要這一場法國大革命式的教育。這就是時代革命的意義所有，這就是香港有機會得以光復的契機。<br />\n諸位兄弟保重！"},{"pid":"89cd88403fcf96e90ae9e32b361d1e2d23b58963","tid":1632112,"uid":30113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:03.000Z","msg":"要繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">好多滲透 保持清醒 唔好被仇恨支配</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"bde4568ee3dba9c37da7a937a106c13ed7d9c89b","tid":1632112,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:27.000Z","msg":"越憤怒時，越要冷靜"},{"pid":"3e66142191fd89e6166a855847c878a0767a41e5","tid":1632112,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818a22526f7db1a13f2fe9f353af2e84446b3903","tid":1632112,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:42.000Z","msg":"Hkers add oil"},{"pid":"0c227accd74f0aa94eba25f59d0fc20ee4325156","tid":1632112,"uid":68092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:10:10.000Z","msg":"對準政權黑警<br />\n<br />\n裝修獅鳥前要諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e805ac6cc7816457258acad554c39f100a13b58","tid":1632112,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"Fear can hold you prisoner. Hope can set you free."},{"pid":"280088262fb9458ecf4372cad8692af168c09c0b","tid":1632112,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5661a4608e5bbd59cb85cd84a9c08de2137f77ca","tid":1632112,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ab549bcdff5e4a82dcb5cab163f9840dfe9cbfbc","tid":1632112,"uid":254596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:37.000Z","msg":"pushhhhh"},{"pid":"514b6333d6ee26716da5c4129c5f1f37f55b73b1","tid":1632112,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:09:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fbc56d3dd9918a398628c6e7361b9f9aa10b0ed","tid":1632112,"uid":94241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:10:50.000Z","msg":"Push!!!!!!"},{"pid":"95184c5215a5d054d75e7cfba9e7d007a05d234f","tid":1632112,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:13:10.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n除左硬爆，仲有好多方法可以用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚十八區一齊文宣開花<br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631757</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8b7f118f9cd8a43cf5018de594c2099fe1d02cc7","tid":1632112,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}